{"tid":975371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港大炒廣東四球 熱血教練郭嘉諾帶隊再贏省港盃","createTime":"2019-01-09T14:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T13:39:43.000Z","uid":40628,"like":110,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fb4d6342b16754729c40fe30fbb85788381b6ba3","tid":975371,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/imagecache/w274/column_images/HKT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fimagecache%2Fw274%2Fcolumn_images%2FHKT.jpg&h=67140d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n省港盃晚上在香港大球場進行，香港在第二回合的比賽以四球淨勝廣東，成功衛冕省港盃，這亦是郭嘉諾連續第二年帶領香港拿下省港盃。<br />\n<br />\n郭嘉諾賽前鼓勵球員要打爭氣波，高叫「100%」，更和球員圍圈激勵士氣。他在比賽期間更幾近沒有坐下來，全程熱血和投入地指揮。<br />\n<br />\n_DSC4092<br />\n<br />\n香港隊首回合作客廣州，一比二不敵廣東，但回到主場香港大球場份外醒神。廣東在上半場已先遭香港先攻入一球，廣東隊後衛涂東旭漏頂，安永佳接應罰球入楔破網，比賽回到起點。在下半場初段，香港後衛梁諾恆接應死球，以頭鎚入波「將功補過」首回合的失誤，涂東旭再次走漏對手，香港隊領先兩球。港隊前鋒袁振昇在56分鐘運球入禁區，搏得對手犯規，並主射十二碼入網。<br />\n<br />\n在領先至三比零時，安永佳和廣東隊球員發生爭執，廣東守門員侯宇更衝往半場加入戰團，最後雙雙被罰紅牌離場。廣東換入後備守門員楊超，但香港隊茹子楠射入世界波，奠定四比零的勝局。"},{"pid":"361e27804c58ee8dd9152cdac3ee1727c87aef3f","tid":975371,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b9f25d2d649f5d5a7a2f1bb79b6ad30e913fd2","tid":975371,"uid":40628,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:41:33.000Z","msg":"We are Hong Kong <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec4c7b9b3b873f5a758b5b8197dd76768c7282d","tid":975371,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba24e3fa59517023aba89ee89cd76991963eaaa","tid":975371,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:00:37.000Z","msg":"打柒支支"},{"pid":"03456738387115512f476368000a2e85c11d5e3a","tid":975371,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce18f1767460e255f30daa4bc827dd5dae55d109","tid":975371,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87507e2a6c0edf205bf66acddea0451be4962e1b","tid":975371,"uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:11:10.000Z","msg":"果然係郭嘉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddca5837e6670f9fbc37e9059c21a96156f169e","tid":975371,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"690b09316d2a0d74c5598ea1544c607ca52c0eda","tid":975371,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":58,"score":-57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:14:54.000Z","msg":"「港獨」分子早已猶如過街老鼠，但仍死不悔改！昨晚「港獨」組織「學生獨立聯盟」公然在旺角街頭舉行所謂的「港獨」集會，除了視梁天琦等暴徒為英雄，事前更聲稱要來一次「大規模社會抗爭計劃嘅預告」，還揚言「以死相搏」云云。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，所謂的「大規模社會抗爭計劃嘅預告」，最後只是向本土民主前線借得旺角暴亂的影片作播放，至於「以死相搏」，就是單純的叫囂「香港獨立」和「以死相搏」了事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最惹人竊笑的，是所謂的集會，僅有學生獨立聯盟發言人呂俊賢、中大學生會會長區倬僖、城大學生會外務副會長劉嘉譽、理大學生會會長林穎恒、學生動源鍾翰林、「港獨」人士鄭俠、「本土派」梁金成等人先後發言。參加者較現場的記者和警員都要少。其餘則是抱著「八卦」心態觀看的途人。整場集會淪為一場「無聊爛騷」。"},{"pid":"af6a77b7c44b6d2dfe18dc4866c9c917c86f2584","tid":975371,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"俾郭sir坐正啦"},{"pid":"41a09bfcd6e2b5e5a0be14c88bf4d347208208b0","tid":975371,"uid":141793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"af6a77b7c44b6d2dfe18dc4866c9c917c86f2584","tid":975371,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"俾郭sir坐正啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:48:13.000Z","msg":"其實值得試下<br />\n不過都係似請出面　外國人空降"},{"pid":"8917bcc84329af5b69481e6765bc9684a7e0748c","tid":975371,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23b7089a123795b3049f5471ea7d4f4ef2b0184","tid":975371,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T17:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632da8e2f1a6a8797c09e062a327c14d7e729a27","tid":975371,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"690b09316d2a0d74c5598ea1544c607ca52c0eda","tid":975371,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":58,"score":-57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:14:54.000Z","msg":"「港獨」分子早已猶如過街老鼠，但仍死不悔改！昨晚「港獨」組織「學生獨立聯盟」公然在旺角街頭舉行所謂的「港獨」集會，除了視梁天琦等暴徒為英雄，事前更聲稱要來一次「大規模社會抗爭計劃嘅預告」，還揚言「以死相搏」云云。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，所謂的「大規模社會抗爭計劃嘅預告」，最後只是向本土民主前線借得旺角暴亂的影片作播放，至於「以死相搏」，就是單純的叫囂「香港獨立」和「以死相搏」了事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最惹人竊笑的，是所謂的集會，僅有學生獨立聯盟發言人呂俊賢、中大學生會會長區倬僖、城大學生會外務副會長劉嘉譽、理大學生會會長林穎恒、學生動源鍾翰林、「港獨」人士鄭俠、「本土派」梁金成等人先後發言。參加者較